The two beautiful princesses are the best friends and luckily they both have got pregnant at the same time. Becoming mommies is the best thing any girl experiences in her life. Elsa and Rapunzel are the two girls who are going to be pregnant and now they need your help in their daily life routine. These both girls are helping each other get ready. But your fashion advice helps them to get prepared perfectly. Join 
Happy Princesses Pregnant Bffs and get ready to help them to spot some beautiful clothes, accessories and hairstyles!

Keep in mind that these both two Disney princesses are expecting babies so try to pick up the items accordingly to make them look amazing in this one of the best HTML5 games for girls. Make sure to dress them up and take care of them their daily routine. Spend the whole day with them and help them to perform multiple activities in this cute caring game! Check if they have taken the vitamins on time and consumed the healthy food items! Do not forget to provide their little ones with the needful care. 

Try to place their favorite headphones on the bellies and help them to be surrounded by the cool environment by planning some beautiful music! Select a wonderful outfit and combine it with a matching hairstyle for each mommy! We hope that you would have great fun in this girls dress-up game.  In case of seeking more fun opportunities, feel free to check out other girl games that are playable on multiple devices, no download required.  Good luck to have the best time online alone or with your friends!!
